---
title: Chermoula Roasted Lamb & Balsamic Sauce with Garlic Veggie Mash & Radish Salad
description: You might need a pair of sunglasses for this meal because it’s blinding, especially with garlic, potato and carrot
combined into a sunset mash. What’s goes best with a mash than a lamb roast of course and this one is succulent, tender and drizzled in a balsamic sauce for a dark tone. Trust us, it tastes just as good as it looks.

